cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper discusses the success and architecture of deep learning methods, which are primarily used in machine learning and artificial intelligence applications. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also touches on the training process of neural networks, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision).
